Pandas is an open source library built on top of NumPy (Python's version of R)

It allows for fast analysis and data cleaning and preparation

It excels in performance and productivity

It has also built in data visualization features

It can work with data from wide variety of sources

pip3 install pandas

Interaction of following with Pandas:

-Series
-Data Frames
-Missing Data
-GroupBy
-Merging, Joining and Concatenating Data Frames
-Operations
-Data Input and Output for csv, excel, SQL files